responses: {"Q0":"Jason is fighting Lymphoma a form of cancer.  He also recently underwent Thyroid surgery.  He has had one round of chemotherapy and several more to come at 21 day intervals.  This is the same form of cancer my sister had so it is close to my heart.  I know he will be in for a rough road ahead as he battles through chemotherapy.  It won't be easy.  His best friend has set up a fundraiser to help alleviate some of the money worries as he goes through this battle. "}
